      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and documented service history from authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of all maintenance records. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
